data.description: Large and comfortable two bed, two bath condo in the beautiful community of Club Villas at Wimbledon. A split floor plan ensure privacy for both bedrooms. The primary bedroom has a walk in closet and en suite bath.  It also has sliding doors to the screened porch.  The living room and dining area are spacious and comfortable. There is a washer and dryer in the kitchen.  The kitchen layout maximizes storage and prep room for the space.  This is a gated community, and features tennis/pickleball courts, a clubhouse, fitness center, and pool. Very convenient to grocery stores, shopping, dining, and the airport.
